  "texts": [
    "Second, we have contributed to the ongoing fair-AI discussion with additional challenges, policy advice, and best practices that resulted from the execution of the NoBIAS project.",
    "We argue that these are, although deemed relevant, not sufficiently developed nor acknowledged in the literature.",
    "These are summarized in Figs.",
    "2, 3, 4, 5, with in parenthesis the reference to the section of the paper where they are discussed in.",
    "While we do not claim for their completeness, we hope that those advices and best practices will contribute to the conventional wisdom in research and practice of managing bias and fairness in AI."
  ]
}